  "texts": [
    "For example, it might be easier to implement for cameras but more challenging for lidar.",
    "Simple solutions like a lightweight filter are capable of rating images, mapping the ratings to keys, and selecting the tuned parameters to switch.",
    "However, it is not as straightforward when dealing with lidar data.",
    "The complexity of lidar data, with its 3D point cloud representation, makes it challenging to use the same methodology to rate, map, and switch parameters as easily as we do with images.",
    "Therefore, we consider the development of a more self-contained approach to be part of our future work."
  ],
